<!-- ================= 详情视图：残局挑战规则详情 ================= -->
<view class="page-container view-container {{currentView === 'detail-puzzle' ? 'active' : ''}}">
    <!-- 头部 -->
    <view class="header">
        <view class="back-btn" bindtap="goBack">❮</view>
        <view class="page-title">残局挑战详则</view>
    </view>

    <!-- Section 1: 游戏目标 -->
    <view class="section-card">
        <view class="section-title purple">游戏目标</view>
        <view class="desc-text">根据系统给出的线索，运用逻辑推理解开 <text class="bold">4位数字密码</text>。每关都有预设线索和步数限制，考验你的推理能力！</view>
        
        <view class="puzzle-mockup">
            <view class="pm-title">找出4位密码</view>
            <view class="pm-clues">
                <view class="pm-clue-row">
                    <view class="pm-clue-nums">
                        <view class="pm-num">1</view>
                        <view class="pm-num">2</view>
                        <view class="pm-num">3</view>
                        <view class="pm-num">4</view>
                    </view>
                    <view class="pm-result"><text class="pm-a">1</text>A <text class="pm-b">2</text>B</view>
                </view>
                <view class="pm-clue-row">
                    <view class="pm-clue-nums">
                        <view class="pm-num">5</view>
                        <view class="pm-num">6</view>
                        <view class="pm-num">7</view>
                        <view class="pm-num">8</view>
                    </view>
                    <view class="pm-result"><text class="pm-a">0</text>A <text class="pm-b">1</text>B</view>
                </view>
            </view>
        </view>
    </view>

    <!-- Section 2: AB提示规则 -->
    <view class="section-card">
        <view class="section-title purple">AB提示规则</view>
        <view class="desc-text">每次猜测后，系统会给出A和B的提示，帮助你逐步缩小答案范围：</view>
        
        <view class="ab-hint-box">
            <view class="ab-hint-item">
                <view class="ab-badge ab-a">A</view>
                <view class="ab-hint-text">
                    <view class="ab-hint-title">数字和位置都对</view>
                    <view class="ab-hint-desc">猜测的数字中，有几个数字不仅数值正确，位置也完全正确</view>
                </view>
            </view>
            <view class="ab-divider"></view>
            <view class="ab-hint-item">
                <view class="ab-badge ab-b">B</view>
                <view class="ab-hint-text">
                    <view class="ab-hint-title">数字对但位置不对</view>
                    <view class="ab-hint-desc">猜测的数字中，有几个数字数值正确，但位置不正确</view>
                </view>
            </view>
        </view>

        <view class="desc-text tip-box">
            <text>💡 </text><text class="bold">举例说明：</text>
            <text>如果答案是 9012，你猜 1234，得到 <text class="highlight">1A 1B</text>：
            1A 表示数字1位置正确，1B 表示数字2存在但位置不对。</text>
        </view>
    </view>

    <!-- Section 3: 体力与星级系统 -->
    <view class="section-card">
        <view class="section-title purple">体力与星级系统</view>
        
        <view class="puzzle-feature-row">
            <view class="pf-icon">⚡</view>
            <view class="pf-content">
                <view class="pf-title">体力消耗</view>
                <view class="pf-desc">每次挑战需消耗 <text class="bold">20体力</text>，体力会随时间恢复（2体力/分钟），也可通过观看广告快速恢复</view>
            </view>
        </view>

        <view class="puzzle-feature-row">
            <view class="pf-icon">⭐</view>
            <view class="pf-content">
                <view class="pf-title">星级评价</view>
                <view class="pf-desc">
                    <text class="star-line"><text class="star">★★★</text> 无复活通关</text>
                    <text class="star-line"><text class="star">★★☆</text> 使用1次复活</text>
                    <text class="star-line"><text class="star">★☆☆</text> 使用2次复活</text>
                </view>
            </view>
        </view>

        <view class="puzzle-feature-row">
            <view class="pf-icon">🎁</view>
            <view class="pf-content">
                <view class="pf-title">通关奖励</view>
                <view class="pf-desc">
                    <text class="reward-line"><text class="star">★★★</text> +30体力</text>
                    <text class="reward-line"><text class="star">★★☆</text> +20体力</text>
                    <text class="reward-line"><text class="star">★☆☆</text> +10体力</text>
                </view>
            </view>
        </view>

        <view class="limit-box purple-box">
            <text>⚠️ 注意：3星完美通关的关卡无法重新挑战，其他星级可消耗体力重新挑战以获取更高星级。</text>
        </view>
    </view>

    <!-- Section 4: 复活机制 -->
    <view class="section-card">
        <view class="section-title purple">复活机制</view>
        <view class="desc-text">步数耗尽时，你可以通过以下方式复活，继续挑战：</view>
        
        <view class="revive-options">
            <view class="revive-item">
                <view class="revive-icon">📤</view>
                <view class="revive-info">
                    <view class="revive-name">分享复活</view>
                    <view class="revive-desc">分享游戏给好友，步数 <text class="bold">+2</text>（每关限1次）</view>
                </view>
            </view>
            <view class="revive-item">
                <view class="revive-icon">📺</view>
                <view class="revive-info">
                    <view class="revive-name">广告复活</view>
                    <view class="revive-desc">观看激励视频，步数 <text class="bold">+3</text>（每关限1次）</view>
                </view>
            </view>
        </view>

        <view class="desc-text tip-box">
            <text>💡 </text><text class="bold">策略提示：</text>
            <text>复活次数会影响最终星级评价，尽量在关键时刻使用，争取3星完美通关！</text>
        </view>
    </view>
</view>

